cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper proposes methods to enhance the performance of human activity recognition systems using ranking and re-ranking techniques. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a training-free re-ranking technique, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with video features, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
